data.description: This immaculately maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the Hidden Forest Subdivision won't last long! Beautiful wood flooring and a cozy fireplace make the living room a great space for entertaining. French doors open to the backyard that is enclosed by a privacy fence, offering a tranquil outdoor space. The kitchen is updated and bright with ample storage space. The split floor plan allows for privacy in the primary bedroom and bathroom.  This fabulous home is located only minutes from shopping, restaurants, and an excellent school district!
